# Privacy Policy

## Anonymity
- You remain anonymous. We do not collect your real name or contact details.

## Chat Data
- Chats are temporary and are not intended to be stored long‑term.  
- Messages may exist in Firebase for a short time as part of technical operation.

## Safety Guidelines
- Do not share personal information (phone number, address, passwords, etc.) with strangers.  
- This app is for adults only.  
- Do not use it for harassment, bullying, hate speech, or illegal activities.

## Media Sharing
- Images, GIFs, and stickers you send are visible to the stranger you are matched with.

## Analytics
- We may use anonymous analytics to improve app performance and reliability.

## Acceptance
- By continuing to use the app, you accept these terms and any future updates to this policy.
